<topic id="ant-transformation-options-tab">
  <title>Options Tab (Ant Transformations)</title>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Options</uicontrol> tab allows you to specify the following options:<dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Working directory</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The path of the current directory of the Ant external process. An <xref
              href="editor-variables.dita#editor-variables" format="dita">editor variable</xref> can
            be inserted for the file path by using the <uicontrol><image
                href="../img/InsertEditorVariables16.png"/>Insert Editor Variables</uicontrol>
            button.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Build file</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The Ant script file that is the input of the Ant external process. An <xref
              href="editor-variables.dita#editor-variables" format="dita">editor variable</xref> can
            be inserted for the file path by using the <uicontrol><image
                href="../img/InsertEditorVariables16.png"/>Insert Editor Variables</uicontrol>
            button.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Build target</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Optionally, you can specify a build target for the Ant script file. If no target is
            specified, the Ant target that is specified as the default in the Ant script file is
            used.</dd>
        </dlentry>
